
  4-site SSH chain, see also L.Stella et al. J. Chem. Phys. 134, 194105 (2011)

  CEID order 0 run:

    ../../src/PolyCEID/PolyCEID input01_o0 >& output01_o0

  CEID order 5 run

    ../../src/PolyCEID/PolyCEID input01_o5 >& output01_o5

  To visualise the effect of resonant electron-ion coupling, open gnuplot and
  type:

  p './positions_run01_o0.dat' u 1:($4-$3) t 'CEID 0' w l lt 1, './positions_run01_o5.dat' u 1:($4-$3) t 'CEID 5' w l lt 3

